Dictator: ^Today, to the glory for our great country, I announce a momentous undertaking!
^Our motherland stands proudly at the forefront of colonizing a new planet.
^It is an expression of our strength and steadfast determination. Together, we undertake this bold endeavor to see our culture and values flourish.
^May pride in our country, our unity and solidarity go with us on this great journey! Long live our country!
